{"tid":1626452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[知己知彼］睇睇反蒙面法先","createTime":"2019-10-05T11:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T11:21:36.000Z","uid":36546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01aa4f5f16e2bbca84d0fe3317dd2495009d5603","tid":1626452,"uid":36546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"琴日出左個蒙面法，就搞到咁大回響，咁究竟係咩黎？<br />\n<br />\n政府文件（如果搵錯請指正）：<a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20192342e/cs220192342119.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F20192342e%2Fcs220192342119.pdf&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=37da1869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/20192342e/cs220192342119.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲，我知雖然大家都未必睇得明法律文件（我都唔識），但睇下都可以了解多啲，知下自己既權利<br />\n<br />\n入面寫咗：<br />\n&middot;任何人不得在身處以下活動時，<span style=\"color: red;\">使用相當可能阻止識辨身分的蒙面物品 </span><br />\n<br />\n&middot;該人當時身處有關集結、集會或遊行，並正在因先前已存在的<span style=\"color: red;\">醫學或健康理由</span>，而使用有關蒙面物品。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;同埋警察好似可以係公眾地方要求除下蒙面物品檢查，呢個時間除左無事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他留俾識法律既巴絲指教"}]}